OL,3,CThames Water hosepipe ban to continue
OL,4,Cafter UK's hottest summer on record
OL,6,FA hosepipe ban covering Oxfordshire,
OL,7,FBerkshire, Wiltshire and
OL,8,FGloucestershire will remain in place
OL,9,Ffor the foreseeable future.
OL,11,FThames Water introduced the
OL,12,Frestrictions on Tuesday 22 July 2025,
OL,13,Fimpacting areas with a postcode
OL,14,Fstarting with OX, GL, SN and RG4, RG8
OL,15,Fand RG9.
OL,17,FCustomers are asked not to use
OL,18,Fhosepipes, including for cleaning
OL,19,Fcars, watering gardens or allotments,
OL,20,Ffilling paddling pools and swimming
OL,21,Fpools or cleaning windows.
