OL,3,CThames Water hosepipe ban to continue
OL,4,Cafter UK's hottest summer on record
OL,6,FIt follows the UK's warmest summer on
OL,7,Frecord, with a mean (average)
OL,8,Ftemperature of 16.10C, surpassing the
OL,9,Fprevious record of15.76Cset in 2018.
OL,11,FNevil Muncaster, Strategic Water
OL,12,FResources Director at Thames Water,
OL,13,Fsaid: "This summer has been the
OL,14,Fhottest on record and in our region
OL,15,Falone, we've had less than half the
OL,16,Frainfall we would expect over the last
OL,17,Ffew months, meaning rivers and
OL,18,Fgroundwater levels in the west of our
OL,19,Fregion are still under significant
OL,20,Fpressure.
