OL,3,CThames Water hosepipe ban to continue
OL,4,Cafter UK's hottest summer on record
OL,6,F"We've welcomed the rain over the past
OL,7,Ffew weeks, which has helped the rivers
OL,8,Fwe use to top up our reservoirs,
OL,9,Fhowever most of this rainfall has been
OL,10,Fsoaked up by the excessively dry
OL,11,Fground and hasn't had a notable impact
OL,12,Fto the groundwater levels which feed
OL,13,Fthe River Thames.
OL,15,F"To restore reservoir levels to
OL,16,Fnormal, we need at least 70% of our
OL,17,Faverage rainfall between now and
OL,18,Fspring.
