OL,3,CThames Water hosepipe ban to continue
OL,4,Cafter UK's hottest summer on record
OL,6,F"Our water resources will take time to
OL,7,Frecover. Consequently, current
OL,8,Fhosepipe restrictions will remain in
OL,9,Fplace.
OL,11,F"We've also seen a faster decline in
OL,12,FLondon's reservoir levels in recent
OL,13,Fweeks and we're closely monitoring the
OL,14,Fsituation to help protect water
OL,15,Fresources ahead of next summer (2026).
OL,17,F"We'd like to thank our customers for
OL,18,Ftheir continued support, saving more
OL,19,Fthan 5 million litres of water each
OL,20,Fday since the hosepipe ban began.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
