OL,3,CThames Water hosepipe ban to continue
OL,4,Cafter UK's hottest summer on record
OL,6,F"We encourage everyone to keep using
OL,7,Fwater wisely to protect our local
OL,8,Frivers, reservoirs, and wildlife.
OL,9,FWe'll keep customers and stakeholders
OL,10,Fupdated as we move through the autumn
OL,11,Fand winter months."
OL,13,FThames Water says that since June 1,
OL,14,Fit has fixed 1500 leaks in the area
OL,15,Faffected by the hosepipe ban.
